4wzO","type":"image","title":null,"desc":{"html":"<p>How do you search vectors ?<\/p>\n"},"image":"https:\/\/on.notist.cloud\/slides\/deck13676\/large-18.jpg","html":null},{"id":"sl_O9nkrn","type":"image","title":null,"desc":{"html":"<p>Architecture of Vector Search<\/p>\n"},"image":"https:\/\/on.notist.cloud\/slides\/deck13676\/large-19.jpg","html":null},{"id":"sl_0TWYkC","type":"image","title":null,"desc":{"html":"<p>knn query\nGET ecommerce\/_search { \u201cquery\u201d : { \u201cbool\u201d: { \u201cmust\u201d: [{ \u201cknn\u201d: { \u201cfield\u201d: \u201cdesc_embbeding\u201d, \u201cnum_candidates\u201d: 50, \u201cquery_vector\u201d: [0.123, 0.244,\u2026]\n} }], \u201cfilter\u201d: { \u201cterm\u201d: { \u201cdepartment\u201d: \u201cwomen\u201d } }\n}\n} }, \u201csize\u201d: 10<\/p>\n"},"image":"https:\/\/on.notist.cloud\/slides\/deck13676\/large-20.png","html":null},{"id":"sl_cnFMcb","type":"image","title":null,"desc":{"html":"<p>Architecture of Vector Search<\/p>\n"},"image":"https:\/\/on.notist.cloud\/slides\/deck13676\/large-21.jpg","html":null},{"id":"sl_F6yAV0","type":"image","title":null,"desc":{"html":"<p>But how does it really work?<\/p>\n"},"image":"https:\/\/on.notist.cloud\/slides\/deck13676\/large-22.jpg","html":null},{"id":"sl_rQgyNP","type":"image","title":null,"desc":{"html":"<p>Similarity\nHuman\nq\ncos(\u03b8) =\nd1 d2 Realistic\n\u03b8\nq\u20d7 \u00d7 d \u20d7\n| q\u20d7 | \u00d7 | d |\u20d7\n_score =\n1 + cos(\u03b8) 2<\/p>\n"},"image":"https:\/\/on.notist.cloud\/slides\/deck13676\/large-23.jpg","html":null},{"id":"sl_TkPmFo","type":"image","title":null,"desc":{"html":"<p>Similarity \u03b8\nSimilar vectors \u03b8 close to 0 cos(\u03b8) close to 1\n1+1 _score = =1 2\n\u03b8\nOrthogonal vectors \u03b8 close to 90\u00b0 cos(\u03b8) close to 0\n1+0 _score = = 0.5 2\n\u03b8\nOpposite vectors \u03b8 close to 180\u00b0 cos(\u03b8) close to -1\n1\u22121 _score = =0 2<\/p>\n"},"image":"https:\/\/on.notist.cloud\/slides\/deck13676\/large-24.jpg","html"